OL,3,CHeathrow offers therapy to locals
OL,4,Caffected by plans to build third runway
OL,6,FHeathrow Airport will offer therapy to
OL,7,Fresidents impacted by the development
OL,8,Fof a third runway.
OL,10,FThe #49 billion project, which has
OL,11,Fstill not fully taken off, will
OL,12,Finvolve demolishing around 750 homes
OL,13,Fand rerouting the M25 between
OL,14,Fjunctions 14 and 15.
OL,16,FHeathrow will offer locals living in
OL,17,Fthe compulsory purchase zone (CPZ)
OL,18,Ffully funded "independent and
OL,19,Fconfidential mental health support,"
OL,20,Fwhich will be delivered by a third
OL,21,Fparty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
