OL,3,CHeathrow offers therapy to locals
OL,4,Caffected by plans to build third runway
OL,6,FExpansion plans promise to increase
OL,7,Fflight capacity by nearly 280,000 a
OL,8,Fyear and create 40,000 jobs.
OL,10,FBecky Coffin, Heathrow's Director of
OL,11,FCommunities and Residential Property,
OL,12,Fsaid: "We acknowledge that the coming
OL,13,Fyears will be incredibly difficult for
OL,14,Fsome, and this support is part of our
OL,15,Fcommitment to be a better neighbour."
OL,17,FHowever, campaigners are concerned
OL,18,Fabout the development's impact on the
OL,19,Fcommunity and the increase in air and
OL,20,Fnoise pollution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
