FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782843506
OL,3,CHeathrow offers therapy to locals
OL,4,Caffected by plans to build third runway
OL,6,FThe airport has said homeowners
OL,7,Fevicted due to the expansion will
OL,8,Freceive compensation at 125 per cent
OL,9,Fof market value plus stamp duty and
OL,10,F"all legal fees in relation to
OL,11,Fpurchasing a new home".
OL,13,FThey have also proposed #550 million
OL,14,Fin funding for noise insulation and
OL,15,Fresidential property compensation if
OL,16,Fthe government backs the development.
OL,18,FHeathrow is aiming to gain planning
OL,19,Fpermission by 2029, with plans for the
OL,20,Fthird runway to come into operation in
OL,21,Fa decade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
