PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782843506
OL,3,CHeathrow offers therapy to locals
OL,4,Caffected by plans to build third runway
OL,6,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,7,Fhas favoured the new runway plans, but
OL,8,Fsaid, "expansion should only proceed
OL,9,Fif it can demonstrate that it will
OL,10,Fcontribute to economic growth... and
OL,11,Fmeet the government's requirements on
OL,12,Fclimate, air quality and noise".
OL,14,FA consultation process between the
OL,15,Fgovernment and the community is
OL,16,Fongoing until September 1.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/4
